              "content": "Each proof row shows:\n\n→ Platform icon (GitHub, Vercel, Lovable, v0, Replit, Bolt)\n→ What was built in plain english\n→ Verification badge from the source\n\nThe score becomes meaningful because you can SEE what earned it.\n\nA random \"724\" means nothing.\n\"47 Claude Code commits verified by GitHub\" means everything.",
